<div class="container"> <div class="row" style="margin-left: 7px;"> <div class="col-md-12 nopadding"> <div class="col-md-12"> <div class="brak-page color-2"> <ol class="breadcrumb" style="margin-bottom: 10px;"> <li><a href="https://www.misrtravel.net"><i class="fa fa-home" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></li> <li class="active">Help &amp; FAQs</li> </ol> </div> </div> </div> <div class="col-md-12"> <div class="col-md-12 nopadding" style="text-align: center;"> <h1><b>Help &amp; FAQs</b></h1> <img class="lazy" data-original="https://www.misrtravel.net/uploads/pages/8563f6943e74b9db9053076ec472f428.jpg" alt="frequently asked questions about Misr travel" title="Help &amp; FAQs" src="https://www.misrtravel.net/uploads/pages/8563f6943e74b9db9053076ec472f428.jpg" style="display: inline;"> </div> </div> <br> <div class="col-md-12">   <div class="col-md-12 nopadding">   <div id="Itinerary"> <div class="panel-group" id="accordion" role="tablist" aria-multiselectable="true">  <div class="panel panel-default"> <div class="panel-heading" role="tab" id="heading0"> <h4 class="panel-title"> <a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse0" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapse0"> <i class="fa fa-calendar-minus-o" aria-hidden="true"></i> Do I have to pay up front? </a> </h4> </div> <div id="collapse0" class="panel-collapse collapse in" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="heading0"> <div class="panel-body st-accr"> <p><span style="font-size:14px;">No. For most packages, we only require a per-person deposit to hold your booking. (The amount varies by package.) This deposit will be applied towards the cost of your package.</span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:14px;">Your balance is due later. The due date will be shown when you book. For most packages, the due date is 30&nbsp;days prior to departure.&nbsp;</span></p> </div> </div> </div>  <div class="panel panel-default"> <div class="panel-heading" role="tab" id="heading1"> <h4 class="panel-title"> <a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse1" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapse1"> <i class="fa fa-calendar-minus-o" aria-hidden="true"></i> What if I need to change or cancel my booking? </a> </h4> </div> <div id="collapse1" class="panel-collapse collapse " role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="heading1"> <div class="panel-body st-accr"> <p><span style="font-size: 14px;">Kindly refer to the price conditions for every tour .</span></p> </div> </div> </div>  <div class="panel panel-default"> <div class="panel-heading" role="tab" id="heading2"> <h4 class="panel-title"> <a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse2" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapse2"> <i class="fa fa-calendar-minus-o" aria-hidden="true"></i> Why are deposits non-refundable? </a> </h4> </div> <div id="collapse2" class="panel-collapse collapse " role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="heading2"> <div class="panel-body st-accr"> <p><span style="font-size:14px;">In order to offer you our tours &amp; packages at such fantastic prices, we make financial commitments to suppliers far in advance of each departure date. These commitments are covered by your deposits and cannot be refunded should you cancel your reservation.&nbsp;</span></p> </div> </div> </div>  <div class="panel panel-default"> <div class="panel-heading" role="tab" id="heading3"> <h4 class="panel-title"> <a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse3" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapse3"> <i class="fa fa-calendar-minus-o" aria-hidden="true"></i> Should I purchase a travel protection plan? </a> </h4> </div> <div id="collapse3" class="panel-collapse collapse " role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="heading3"> <div class="panel-body st-accr"> <p><span style="font-size:14px;">We recommend the purchase of travel protection to all of our customers to help protect you and your travel investment against the unexpected.</span></p> </div> </div> </div>  <div class="panel panel-default"> <div class="panel-heading" role="tab" id="heading4"> <h4 class="panel-title"> <a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse4" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapse4"> <i class="fa fa-calendar-minus-o" aria-hidden="true"></i> Why do I have to pay more to travel solo? </a> </h4> </div> <div id="collapse4" class="panel-collapse collapse " role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="heading4"> <div class="panel-body st-accr"> <p><span style="font-size:14px;">Our packages include Solo accommodations - stated as " One person&nbsp;travelling alone"&nbsp;</span></p> </div> </div> </div>  <div class="panel panel-default"> <div class="panel-heading" role="tab" id="heading5"> <h4 class="panel-title"> <a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse5" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapse5"> <i class="fa fa-calendar-minus-o" aria-hidden="true"></i> Can you help me find a roommate? </a> </h4> </div> <div id="collapse5" class="panel-collapse collapse " role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="heading5"> <div class="panel-body st-accr"> <p><span style="font-size:14px;">We will try but it will be subject to availability .</span></p> </div> </div> </div>  <div class="panel panel-default"> <div class="panel-heading" role="tab" id="heading6"> <h4 class="panel-title"> <a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse6" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapse6"> <i class="fa fa-calendar-minus-o" aria-hidden="true"></i> What forms of payment do you accept? </a> </h4> </div> <div id="collapse6" class="panel-collapse collapse " role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="heading6"> <div class="panel-body st-accr"> <p><span style="font-size:14px;">We accept Credit cards (VISA, Master Card), and payment through bank transfers to our account.</span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:14px;"><b>To pay your deposit</b>: the easiest, fastest and safest way is with your credit card or Payfort&nbsp;account using our secure online booking system. but we cannot hold your place until we receive this payment.</span></p>

<p><span style="font-size:14px;"><b>To make your final payment</b>: we encourage you To pay with your credit card or Payfort&nbsp;account, you may use our&nbsp;secure payment form.&nbsp;</span></p> </div> </div> </div>  <div class="panel panel-default"> <div class="panel-heading" role="tab" id="heading7"> <h4 class="panel-title"> <a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse7" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapse7"> <i class="fa fa-calendar-minus-o" aria-hidden="true"></i> Can I bring my children? </a> </h4> </div> <div id="collapse7" class="panel-collapse collapse " role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="heading7"> <div class="panel-body st-accr"> <p><span style="font-size:14px;">Sure, our tours are safe for children.</span></p> </div> </div> </div>  <div class="panel panel-default"> <div class="panel-heading" role="tab" id="heading8"> <h4 class="panel-title"> <a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse8" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapse8"> <i class="fa fa-calendar-minus-o" aria-hidden="true"></i> How many people will I be traveling with? </a> </h4> </div> <div id="collapse8" class="panel-collapse collapse " role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="heading8"> <div class="panel-body st-accr"> <p><span style="font-size:14px;">Our philosophy based on private tailor made packages so your package is private .</span></p> </div> </div> </div>  <div class="panel panel-default"> <div class="panel-heading" role="tab" id="heading9"> <h4 class="panel-title"> <a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse9" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapse9"> <i class="fa fa-calendar-minus-o" aria-hidden="true"></i> Will somebody accompany our group? </a> </h4> </div> <div id="collapse9" class="panel-collapse collapse " role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="heading9"> <div class="panel-body st-accr"> <p><span style="font-size:14px;">You will be always accompanied by a private speaking tour guide except during Internal flights &amp; Sleeping train.</span></p> </div> </div> </div>  <div class="panel panel-default"> <div class="panel-heading" role="tab" id="heading10"> <h4 class="panel-title"> <a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse10" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapse10"> <i class="fa fa-calendar-minus-o" aria-hidden="true"></i> Do all of your tours include flights? Can I book my own? </a> </h4> </div> <div id="collapse10" class="panel-collapse collapse " role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="heading10"> <div class="panel-body st-accr"> <p><span style="font-size:14px;">Most of our packages includes only Internal flights in Egypt or Sleeping train , <strong>&amp; Not Includes the International flights.</strong></span></p> </div> </div> </div>  <div class="panel panel-default"> <div class="panel-heading" role="tab" id="heading11"> <h4 class="panel-title"> <a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse11" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapse11"> <i class="fa fa-calendar-minus-o" aria-hidden="true"></i> Can I join a tour late or leave it early? </a> </h4> </div> <div id="collapse11" class="panel-collapse collapse " role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="heading11"> <div class="panel-body st-accr"> <p><span style="font-size:14px;">Our tours is private so you will not have to join a tour.&nbsp;</span></p> </div> </div> </div>  <div class="panel panel-default"> <div class="panel-heading" role="tab" id="heading12"> <h4 class="panel-title"> <a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse12" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapse12"> <i class="fa fa-calendar-minus-o" aria-hidden="true"></i> How are seats assigned on my flights? Can I request specific seats ahead of time? </a> </h4> </div> <div id="collapse12" class="panel-collapse collapse " role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="heading12"> <div class="panel-body st-accr"> <p><span style="font-size:14px;">Our packages&nbsp;includes only internal&nbsp;flights, &amp; for internal flights we can not assign seats.&nbsp;</span></p> </div> </div> </div>  <div class="panel panel-default"> <div class="panel-heading" role="tab" id="heading13"> <h4 class="panel-title"> <a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse13" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapse13"> <i class="fa fa-calendar-minus-o" aria-hidden="true"></i> Will I earn frequent flyer miles? </a> </h4> </div> <div id="collapse13" class="panel-collapse collapse " role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="heading13"> <div class="panel-body st-accr"> <p>You will get your flyer miles while making your flight reservation from the carrier.</p> </div> </div> </div>  <div class="panel panel-default"> <div class="panel-heading" role="tab" id="heading14"> <h4 class="panel-title"> <a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse14" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapse14"> <i class="fa fa-calendar-minus-o" aria-hidden="true"></i> Can I use frequent flyer miles to upgrade to business class? </a> </h4> </div> <div id="collapse14" class="panel-collapse collapse " role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="heading14"> <div class="panel-body st-accr"> <p><span style="font-size:14px;">This depends on the carrier &amp; its policy.</span></p> </div> </div> </div>  <div class="panel panel-default"> <div class="panel-heading" role="tab" id="heading15"> <h4 class="panel-title"> <a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse15" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapse15"> <i class="fa fa-calendar-minus-o" aria-hidden="true"></i> How much baggage can I take? </a> </h4> </div> <div id="collapse15" class="panel-collapse collapse " role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="heading15"> <div class="panel-body st-accr"> <p><span style="font-size:14px;">For the International flight it will be according to the type booking&nbsp;policy , &amp; concerning the Internal flight&nbsp;you can have just 1 piece with maximum of 20 kilograms (international dimensions).</span></p> </div> </div> </div>  <div class="panel panel-default"> <div class="panel-heading" role="tab" id="heading16"> <h4 class="panel-title"> <a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse16" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapse16"> <i class="fa fa-calendar-minus-o" aria-hidden="true"></i> Do i need a Visa to travel to Egypt? </a> </h4> </div> <div id="collapse16" class="panel-collapse collapse " role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="heading16"> <div class="panel-body st-accr"> <main>
<p><span style="font-size:14px;">Kindly refer to our Visa section in "About us" .</span></p>
</main>

