</footer> </div> </div> </div>  <div class="panel panel-default"> <div class="panel-heading" role="tab" id="heading17"> <h4 class="panel-title"> <a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse17" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapse17"> <i class="fa fa-calendar-minus-o" aria-hidden="true"></i> Is tipping a custom in Egypt? </a> </h4> </div> <div id="collapse17" class="panel-collapse collapse " role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="heading17"> <div class="panel-body st-accr"> <p>Yes, it is a custom in Egypt as who works in tourism field expects a tip as an appreciation for the good service he offered.</p> </div> </div> </div>  </div> </div> </div>   </div> </div> </div>
